  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Doomed Detective Game</strong> is a first-person detective action game. In this game, you take on the role of a detective who arrives in the town of Redrock to investigate a very mysterious crime.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/685fe0d352d1eb488b2230f72b1f3566.poster.avif?t=1742925284\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/685fe0d352d1eb488b2230f72b1f3566.webm?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/685fe0d352d1eb488b2230f72b1f3566.mp4?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The town is populated with residents, and one of them is blatantly lying and hiding the fact that they are the culprit! Your task is to explore the town, find evidence, talk to the residents, and uncover the murderer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/789f551c2592415d2fd31fba1f487686.poster.avif?t=1742925284\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/789f551c2592415d2fd31fba1f487686.webm?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/789f551c2592415d2fd31fba1f487686.mp4?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The most exciting feature is that every resident in this town is powered by artificial intelligence, and you can talk to them using your microphone! Ask them where they were at the time of the murder, what clues they have, and so on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/51e3b327351827181e047f84066cc6ff.poster.avif?t=1742925284\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/51e3b327351827181e047f84066cc6ff.webm?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/51e3b327351827181e047f84066cc6ff.mp4?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to this, the game offers side quests, puzzles, mini-games, and much more! Play dice in the bar, shoot at cans, and gather additional information along the way!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/bd94fa46380326803708a7259c4d4e81.poster.avif?t=1742925284\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/bd94fa46380326803708a7259c4d4e81.webm?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/bd94fa46380326803708a7259c4d4e81.mp4?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Doomed Detective Game</strong> is a first-person detective action game. In this game, you take on the role of a detective who arrives in the town of Redrock to investigate a very mysterious crime.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/685fe0d352d1eb488b2230f72b1f3566.poster.avif?t=1742925284\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/685fe0d352d1eb488b2230f72b1f3566.webm?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/685fe0d352d1eb488b2230f72b1f3566.mp4?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The town is populated with residents, and one of them is blatantly lying and hiding the fact that they are the culprit! Your task is to explore the town, find evidence, talk to the residents, and uncover the murderer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/789f551c2592415d2fd31fba1f487686.poster.avif?t=1742925284\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/789f551c2592415d2fd31fba1f487686.webm?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/789f551c2592415d2fd31fba1f487686.mp4?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The most exciting feature is that every resident in this town is powered by artificial intelligence, and you can talk to them using your microphone! Ask them where they were at the time of the murder, what clues they have, and so on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/51e3b327351827181e047f84066cc6ff.poster.avif?t=1742925284\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/51e3b327351827181e047f84066cc6ff.webm?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/51e3b327351827181e047f84066cc6ff.mp4?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to this, the game offers side quests, puzzles, mini-games, and much more! Play dice in the bar, shoot at cans, and gather additional information along the way!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/bd94fa46380326803708a7259c4d4e81.poster.avif?t=1742925284\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/bd94fa46380326803708a7259c4d4e81.webm?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361180/extras/bd94fa46380326803708a7259c4d4e81.mp4?t=1742925284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
